Package ch.epfl.lis.wingj

Implements the main classes of WingJ.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ImagePlusManager
    Image manager for WingJ for handling multiple ImagePlus objects.
    WingJ
    Main class of WingJ.
    WJFolderOpener
    Modified version of ij.plugin.FolderOpener to access important variables.
    WJImages
    Represents a stack of images (3D image).
    WJImagesMask
    Shows an ImagePlus and provides the tools to draw a mask.
    WJMessage
    Shows a message in a single JDialog.
    WJPlugIn
    Runs a Singleton instance of WingJ.
    WJSettings
    Offers global parameters (settings) and functions used by WingJ.
    WJStructureViewer
    Displays a Structure object (+ information overlay) on top of an image.
    WJSystem
    Biological sysmtem (organ system or body system).
    WJSystemManager
    Lists the systems (biological organisms or organs) implemented in WingJ.
